Tatyana Chernova failed a drugs test two years before the 2011 World Championships . 
  Jessica Ennis-Hill beat Chernova by 129 points in South Korea in 2011 . 
  Chernova was banned but allowed to keep her world title and won silver at the Olympics . 
  Ennis Hill has written to the IAAF to ask if she can win gold from 2011 . 
  She believes it is unfair that Chernova has been banned but kept her title . 
  The Brit also criticised Nike for sponsoring drugs cheat Justin Gatlin . 
 